<details>
<summary>ðŸ”§ Configuration</summary>

```bash
export ALLOY_MODEL=gpt-5-mini
export ALLOY_TEMPERATURE=0.2
export ALLOY_MAX_TOOL_TURNS=10
```

Or in Python:

```python
from alloy import configure
configure(model="gpt-5-mini", temperature=0.2)
```

</details>

